<td valign="top"><strong>Joy&nbsp;Begbie</strong>:</td>
<td>that was a <span class="caps">DIRTY</span> slo-mo of <a href="http://cache.boston.com/bonzai-fba/Globe_Photo/2007/10/22/1193026512_2505.jpg">Tek and Pap</a></td>
</tr>
